text:
Thank you so much for today!
Let's definitely meet again sometime!

(...Huh?
Wait, was that just now one of the staff members...?)

The person from earlier wasn't an event staff member,
but rather an employee of this facility...
They're apparently a fan of Houkura!

They said they're happy that Houkura
came to their hometown!

I see...!
It's great that they "came to meet us"...

Yes! And I thought, in order to meet them again,
we need to work hard to come back here!
